        "richtext_b9DWKE": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3>Lucira Jewelry - Shop Certified Lab Grown Diamond Jewelry Online</h3><p>Founded with a mission to transform the world of diamonds, Lucira is your go‑to destination for lab‑grown jewelry. We bring conscious luxury to life, blending timeless elegance with ethical innovation. Explore our curated collection of rings, earrings, pendants, bracelets, and necklaces, each piece crafted for brilliance, beauty, and responsibility.</p><h3>India’s Trusted Lab Grown Diamond Brand</h3><p>Lucira Jewelry is proud to be one of India’s leading companies in Lab Grown Diamonds. Whether it’s a gift, a milestone, or a personal treat, our certified and conflict‑free diamonds offer complete peace of mind. Plus, enjoy the freedom to exchange or upgrade anytime because your style deserves to evolve with you.</p><h3>Seamless Online Jewelry Shopping</h3><p>Your shopping experience with Lucira Jewelry is designed for simplicity. Use smart filters to browse by diamond shape, metal color, carat weight, price, or setting style, making your decision effortless and tailored to your preferences.</p><h3>Certified & Ethical Jewelry</h3><p>Every piece from Lucira Jewelry comes with an IGI Certification, ensuring authenticity, quality, and peace of mind. With 100% ethically created Lab Grown Diamonds, we promise sustainability without compromising, no mining, no conflict, just pure brilliance.</p><h3>Crafted to Last, Designed to Shine</h3><p>Every design at Lucira Jewelry is thoughtfully made to celebrate your everyday as well as extravagant moments and milestones. With timeless aesthetics and expert craftsmanship, our jewelry isn’t just beautiful, it’s made to be cherished for all the years to come.</p>"
          }
        }
